<div class="pager">
	<style type="text/css">
	.upload-row{
		border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
	}
	.upload-row > div{
		text-align: center;
	}
	.s300{
		max-width: 300px;
		max-height: 300px;
	}
	.s260{
		width: 260px;
		height: 260px;
	}
	.s200{
		width: 200px;
		height: 200px;
	}
	.s100{
		width: 100px;
		height: 100px;
	}
	.s50{
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
	}
	.review{
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.review img{
		position: relative;
	}
	</style>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/uploadify/uploadify.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/uploadify/jquery.imgareaselect.css" />
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/uploadify/jquery.uploadify.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/uploadify/jquery.imgareaselect.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/uploadify/custom-upload.js"></script>

	<div class="row upload-row">
		<div class="col-md-5" style="border-right: 1px solid #ccc;min-height:300px;">
			<img class="s300" id="cut-area" src="/images/defaults/avatar.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-7">
			<div class="row">
				<%= @current_user.username %>
				<p>您上传的图片将自动生成3种尺寸头像，请注意中小尺寸的头像是否清晰</p>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="review s200">
						<img class="s200" src="/images/defaults/avatar.jpg">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="review s100">
							<img class="s100" src="/images/defaults/avatar.jpg">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row" style="margin-top: 40px">
						<div class="review s50">
							<img class="s50" src="/images/defaults/avatar.jpg">
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="upload-div" style="margin: 20px 0;">
		<input class="form-control" id="upload-file">
		<p>仅支持JPG、GIF、PNG格式，文件小于10M。</p>
		<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn-default btn gogo">开始上传</a>
	</div>
</div>